1. Moramo preduzeti mere zaštite od virusa. (*mere*) (We must take measures to protect ourselves from the virus.)
2. Ona je bila izuzetno precizna u svojim merama. (*merama*) (She was extremely precise in her measurements.)
3. Njihove mere štednje urodile su plodom. (*merama*) (Their austerity measures have borne fruit.)
4. Država je uvela stroge mere karantina. (*mera*) (The state has introduced strict quarantine measures.)
5. Mere koje su preduzete nisu bile dovoljne. (*mere*) (The measures taken were not sufficient.)
6. On je imao meru u svemu što je radio. (*meru*) (He had a sense of proportion in everything he did.)
7. Molim te, izmeri dužinu ovog stola. (*izmeri*) (Please measure the length of this table.)
8. Oni su doneli odluku da mere alkohol u krvi vozača. (*mere*) (They decided to measure the alcohol in the driver's blood.)
9. Mera ne može biti ista za sve ljude. (*mera*) (The measure cannot be the same for everyone.)
10. Ona je preduzela mere da se osigura od krađe. (*mere*) (She took measures to protect herself from theft.)